            {
                "__class__": "WallInscription",
                "__module__": "objects",
                "props": {
                    "name": "Configuration Board",
                    "description": "A broad stone panel etched with precise lettering. READ to see the current combat test configuration.",
                    "idle_message": "A configuration board is mounted on the wall.",
                    "hidden": false,
                    "hide_factor": 0,
                    "discovery_message": "a configuration board etched into the stone!",
                    "announce": "A configuration board is mounted on the wall.",
                    "keywords": ["read", "examine", "inspect", "view", "check"],
                    "events": [],
                    "tile": null,
                    "player": null,
                    "text": "=== COMBAT TESTING ARENA — Active Configuration ===\n\nThis board reflects config_combat_testing.ini at last load.\nEdit that file and restart to change the scenario.\n\nARENAS:\n  East  → Fodder Pit      (Slime, CaveBat — weak/fodder enemies)\n  East→East → The Crucible    (KingSlime, Lurker — boss/tank)\n  South → Ally Courtyard  (Gorran + Slime — ally + enemy)\n  South→East → Status Chamber  (Pell — status-effect dummy, all resistances stripped)\n\nINTERACT WITH THE ADJUTANT to adjust Jean's stats at runtime.\nLOOT the Equipment Rack to change your loadout.\n\nAll arenas loop back to this Proving Grounds via the exit in the opposite direction."
                }
            }
        ],
        "symbol": "★"
