    "(1, 1)": {
        "id": "tile_1_1",
        "title": "EmptyCave",
        "description": "The mist here is perfectly still. At the centre of the space stands a featureless shape — neither quite a figure nor a shadow. It does not breathe. It does not speak. It waits.\n\nThis is the Status Chamber. Pell, the test dummy, has every status resistance stripped to zero. Every debuff will land. Use this arena for testing states.py interactions: poison, stun, slow, doom, enflamed — anything and everything. Go west to the Ally Courtyard or north to the Fodder Pit.",
